&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Engineering, Computer Science, Electrical Engineering, Robotics or a related field and 2+ years of relevant experience, Master&#39;s degree, or PhD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to write well-structured, maintainable

