&lt;p&gt;One of the keys to delivering an ADAS driving experience is an accurate, up-to-date HD map that describes the world around us. This map, collected onboard our vehicles and processed by the Data Services Operations team, must meet intense quality standards achieved through structured workflows, rigorous policy and attention to detail. Along with providing HD map production, the Map Operations team supports and enables data-driven decision making by providing GIS analysis to teams across Ford and Latitude.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly skilled and motivated Data Services Analyst to join our team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for quality controlling map data, processing automation feedback, and crafting best practices related to Geographic Information Systems (GIS).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;This contract will be 1 year (12 months) in duration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
