&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute quality control functions in Latitude’s HD map data pipeline to ensure accuracy and consistency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide automation feedback to improve efficiency of Map Operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and ensure the quality of GIS data and related processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyzing spatial data through the use of mapping software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll need to succeed:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in GIS software such as ArcGIS, QGIS, or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical and problem-solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and teamwork abilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in quality control and data management is preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work 100% at desk in a 2D and 3D virtual environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in GIS, Geography, Environmental Science, or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working in an AI/self-driving setting or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience sourcing and federating third party data for spatial analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
