&lt;li&gt;Ability to work onsite in Greenville, SC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong understanding of the autonomous vehicle software stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competency understanding performance requirements for autonomous systems&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to write test documentation for test cases and engineering processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with ADAS automation testing products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in writing Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using dashboarding software such as Looker or Superset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

