&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet the team:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Mission Analyst is a senior-level technical role responsible for executing complex vehicle evaluation missions independently. You will serve as the primary link between the field and the engineering team, managing the vehicle’s software state, troubleshooting system failures in real-time, and providing high-fidelity data. This role eliminates the need for an engineer to be present in the vehicle during most test cycles and requires a degree of technical literacy regarding vehicle software architecture.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Independent Mission Execution:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead and execute comprehensive test routes and maneuvers based on engineering test plans without on-site supervision. Precisely document test cases and suggest product improvements based on field observations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Software Management &amp;amp; Diagnostics:&lt;/strong&gt; Utilize in-house and industry-standard diagnostic tools (e.g., CANalyzer, Vehicle Spy) to perform software updates, module flashing, and configuration changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Triaging &amp;amp; Bug Reporting:&lt;/strong&gt; Identify and document software defects in Jira. Create detailed tickets including reproduction steps and environmental conditions; manage the bug lifecycle by verifying fixes with the development team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Validation &amp;amp; Maintenance:&lt;/strong&gt; Test and validate prototype firmware across platforms. Service and maintain instrumentation systems, firmware interfaces, sensor installations, and vehicle wire harnesses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Troubleshooting: &lt;/strong&gt;Troubleshoot system level Issues, documenting &amp;amp; escalating clear reproduction steps for failure modes. May require the ability to rapidly learn new tools and technologies in a fast-paced, evolving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Data Acquisition:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor and manage onboard data logging equipment to ensure all necessary signals are captured correctly. Execute commands or scripts in a Linux terminal to gather diagnostic data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leadership &amp;amp; Coaching:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversee small shifts or groups, providing coaching and feedback to team members to ensure efficiency and a culture of safety&lt;/li&gt;
